text: Thanks for Coming (Spanish: Gracias por venir) is a 2023 Chilean drama movie directed by first time director Taiyo Yamazaki and starring Daniel Candia, Alejandro Trejo, Alejandra Yáñez, América Navarro and Roberto Villena. ==Other websites== * Category:2023 drama movies Category:Chilean movies Category:Movies set in Chile Category:Movies about death Category:Movies about families
title: Thanks for Coming
